ent-AU14ProdigyFatigues = prodigy fatigues
    .desc = Standard-issue Prodigy Security Forces fatigues.
ent-AU14ProdigyFatiguesRU = Prodigy Armed Repair Team specialized fatigues
    .desc = Standard-issue Prodigy Armed Repair Team fatigues. The PART-SF is a specialized uniform designed for Prodigy Security Corp's Armed Repair Teams, who are responsible for maintaining and repairing equipment in high-risk environments. The uniform features reinforced padding on the knees and elbows, as well as multiple pockets for carrying tools and supplies. It also includes a built-in harness system for attaching additional gear and equipment.
